<span id="freeTextContainer11166601598188417747">Gorgeously illustrated children&apos;s picture book focusing on a boy who runs away from home because he&apos;s bullied for being clumsy and, of course, clumsiness is exactly what saves the day.<br/><br/>It&apos;s a lovely story with a moral, and I believe it would be best for kids in grades 1-3, (though it might have to be read to them).</span>
  <span id="freeText11166601598188417747" style="display:none">Gorgeously illustrated children's picture book focusing on a boy who runs away from home because he's bullied for being clumsy and, of course, clumsiness is exactly what saves the day.<br /><br />It's a lovely story with a moral, and I believe it would be best for kids in grades 1-3, (though it might have to be read to them).</span>
