          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1123139420" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8056900551587153756">This is a beautifully illustrated short children&apos;s story about a boy who feels inept, but becomes a hero to his town. After being teased for not being able to skate, Jackie runs away and becomes lost. As he tries to find his way home, his bumbling actually helps him and helps him to help his town. The writing is lovely to read and Jackie&apos;s story is inspirational and appealing to readers of all ages. </span>
  <span id="freeText8056900551587153756" style="display:none">This is a beautifully illustrated short children's story about a boy who feels inept, but becomes a hero to his town. After being teased for not being able to skate, Jackie runs away and becomes lost. As he tries to find his way home, his bumbling actually helps him and helps him to help his town. The writing is lovely to read and Jackie's story is inspirational and appealing to readers of all ages. </span>
  <a data-text-id="8056900551587153756" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


